These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, puzzles, drawing, filmmaking
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, chef, teacher, paramedic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, blues, indie, pop
4 different pets are kept: mouse, turtle, lizard, ferret
1. the chef is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the fan of indie is the doctor##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the chef##1
5. the teacher is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the chef is the owner of the mouse##1
8. the fan of blues is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting  | filmmaking  | puzzles | drawing |
| Job           | chef | doctor | paramedic  | teacher  |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | indie      | funk | blues      |
| Pet           | mouse          | turtle     | lizard    | ferret     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, coffee, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: lemon, onion, potato, watermelon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, electronic, hip-hop, country
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, soccer, climbing, sailing
1. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1
2. the fan of country is the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person eating potato is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person eating onion##1
5. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
6. the person drinking coffee is the fan of hip-hop##1
7. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
9. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | coffee     | soy-milk       | hot-chocolate | mirinda        |
| Food          | watermelon     | onion       | potato   | lemon   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop      | electronic       | country     | d&b    |
| Sport         | climbing | sailing | skiing | soccer |

