.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, iced-tea, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, firefighter, doctor, pilot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, satire, drama, fantasy
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, horse, hamster
 1. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the hamster##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 7. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the firefighter##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the manager##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | milk | almond-milk       | sprite        | iced-tea        |
| Job           | firefighter   | doctor | manager   | pilot |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster     | satire    | fantasy | drama        |
| Pet           | horse         | goldfish  | hamster       | goat         |

