.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, dressmaker, librarian, chef
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, classical, salsa, country
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, indonesian, polish, french
4 different pets are kept: frog, pony, lizard, goat
1. the polish is on the left of the doctor##1
2. the librarian is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
4. the chef is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of classical##1
6. the fan of country is on the right of the dressmaker##1
7. the chef is on the right of the doctor##1
8. the malaysian is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the lizard is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Job           | dressmaker   | doctor  | chef | librarian |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | country       | classical       | gospel     |
| Nationality   | polish       | french    | indonesian     | malaysian  |
| Pet           | pony     | lizard | goat     | frog         |

