.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, journalist, librarian, lawyer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, musical, western, comedy
There are 4 different nationalities: german, australian, chinese, american
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, skiing, baseball, climbing
1. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the mechanic##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
4. the australian is on the left of the german##1
5. the american is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the person who's sport is climbing is the chinese##1
7. the german is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
8. the journalist is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
9. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Job           | mechanic  | librarian    | journalist | lawyer |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | musical    | thriller         | comedy    |
| Nationality   | australian   | german     | chinese          | american      |
| Sport         | skiing | swimming | climbing      | baseball      |

