.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, cauliflower, corn, papaya
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, entrepreneur, scientist, dressmaker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, western, horror, zombie
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, guinea-pig, goat
 1. the person eating corn is the person watching spy movies##1
 2. the person eating apricot is the person watching western movies##1
 3. the pilot is the person watching spy movies##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating apricot##1
 5. the person watching horror movies is the dressmaker##1
 6. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
 7. the scientist is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 8. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 9. the scientist is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | apricot  | papaya | corn     | cauliflower |
| Job           | scientist  | dressmaker      | pilot | entrepreneur    |
| Movie-Genre   | western | horror  | spy    | zombie  |
| Pet           | guinea-pig   | goat       | bird       | dog      |

