.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, reading, writing, filmmaking
4 different pets are kept: mouse, dog, cat, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, skateboard, car, bike
 1. the owner of the mouse is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the car##1
 8. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | milk | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate    | juice |
| Hobby       | rock-climbing | writing    | filmmaking | reading |
| Pet         | dog   | cat  | rabbit        | mouse    |
| Transport   | bike   | skateboard | helicopter    | car |

