.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, cola, iced-tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, fisherman, dressmaker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, adventure, disaster, comedy
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, taxi, subway, boat
1. the fisherman is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the bartender is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person driving the train##1
7. the engineer is the person driving the train##1
8. the person driving the subway is the person drinking soy-milk##1
9. the person driving the boat is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | soy-milk         | cola        | almond-milk      |
| Job           | engineer | bartender | fisherman  | dressmaker  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster    | crime     | adventure | comedy     |
| Transport     | train        | subway     | taxi     | boat |

