.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, sprite, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, gardening, dancing, collecting
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, japanese, nigerian, pakistani
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, handball, lacrosse, parkour
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking sprite is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the japanese##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
7. the pakistani is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
8. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person drinking milk##1
9. the dutch is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | water     | milk           | fanta    | sprite    |
| Hobby         | dancing  | gardening | singing  | collecting |
| Nationality   | nigerian     | dutch     | japanese | pakistani   |
| Sport         | parkour | baseball     | handball | lacrosse     |

