 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 8. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the fan of blues##1
10. the person eating plum is the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
